        "gggXEdXFdqh_text": "<p>Pure marine collagen, designed to support smoother skin, stronger hair, and a naturally healthy glow.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Every scoop delivers 5g of high-quality collagen peptides to nourish your beauty routine from the inside out — without adding extra steps to your day.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Simple.<br>Effective.<br>Made to be taken daily.</p>"
